room_title: Escape room "Katherine's Asylum Escape" by The Exit Game in San Antonio
room_address: 5720 Bandera Rd STE 23, San Antonio, TX 78238
room_description: Your group of psychoanalysts has been appointed to uncover the mystery of a missing patient at Stonehearst asylum. During the investigation, the hospital has initiated a lockdown. Unraveling the clues, you realize that Katherine, the missing girl, was headed somewhere. Can you find out where she's going and escape with 60 minutes left on the clock?
